# .dockerignore — keep the Docker build context lean and host-platform artifacts OUT of the image
# builds (deploy/Dockerfile.backend + deploy/Dockerfile.frontend build from the repo root). Host
# node_modules / target are platform-specific and must be reinstalled inside the linux builder.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.__mf__temp
backend/target
.git
**/*.log
e2e/node_modules
e2e/cypress/videos
e2e/cypress/screenshots
docs/learn-site/node_modules
docs/learn-site/dist
**/.DS_Store
handoff
ai-logging/*conversation*.md
